Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受引導之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊一切都還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,除了訓練還是訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都順利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們一同前來的魔導士們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是來帶迪蘭度回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向被魔導士所忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不清楚詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是在嫉妒弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也討厭魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣批評魔導士喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經擔任過魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是想著能夠再見到您…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們真是感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就來為我效力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了您而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費了好大的功夫才發現\N原來這是用幻之月的文字寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺,拜託您就別再鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,被寨巴哈盯上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不會有好下場的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來要到幻之谷去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搭這艘船回帕拉斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨物沒了,您又不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要我怎麼向老爺交代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你寫張條子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要說我跟蜜拉娜公主在一起就不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會去的,因為亞連要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我得去?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是你老爸拋棄妻小\N甚至一切財產才找到的幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事在阿斯多利亞可是出了名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連我也聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷是龍神人的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看看我體內龍神人之血的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有它和艾斯卡弗洛尼又有著什麼樣的牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不曉得究竟是什麼機緣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群與幻之谷有關的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水晶北東之年,綠十二之月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正朝從未有人探訪過的黑暗大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加爾德大陸前去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,幻之谷一定就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能找到自己長年追尋的"誕生奇跡之力"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,就是"亞特蘭提斯之力"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了,舵根本不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種暴風雨中根本就沒辦法航行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長,情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石的溫度降不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是龍神的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訑不許人類進入這片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒把船掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟當初說的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經支付你要求的酬勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去船會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也很清楚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經將自己的性命賣給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不曉得過了幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦朧之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了那名少女的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了那名少女的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加爾德大陸\N出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神在引導我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那年輕歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於離奇的命運所引導的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後突如其來的別離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認深深刻畫在我心中對那名少女的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都在幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有我所追尋的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不惜拋家棄子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是為了要找一個女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸還挺有意思的啊\N什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少強過我那個只會數鈔票的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很欣賞這種生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有任何線索嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是你們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們千萬別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…現在還是會作那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會夢到自己上學前和以往一樣在車站等著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後小瞳就會跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻總是只夢到那裏就醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會夢到小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有遇上困難但那孩子不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面除了海還是海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續筆直前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸說是這個方位沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的話可信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長都說要相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能硬著頭皮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派魯,你那邊情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要組裝從德萊甸的人型裝甲上\N取下來的操演宮零件挺花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了,這顆螺絲就是栓不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,可別弄壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青十六之月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇烈的暴風雪與驚險的巖場阻擋了我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是在測試向謎團挑戰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一名老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有人也跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信幻之谷的存在而旅行尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問他叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他叫艾薩克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我從未跟人提起過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過告訴你們或許比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾聽家母說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也恰好是在小瞳這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在參加完夏日慶典回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她整個人突然被光芒所籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來自己已身處一個從未見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薩克的話相當有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在尋找幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著亞特蘭提斯之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最令人驚訝的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薩克跟那名女孩一樣說自己是從幻之月來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是家母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會是幻之月人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了要斷絕一切束縛才開始這段旅程的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你的雙眸卻讓我覺得這一切都毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意原諒我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞德羅福斯將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來請求您允許讓迪蘭度回國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔導士竟然會徵詢我的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說他是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他原本就是你們這些魔導士交給我的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把理由告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到軍師弗肯如此通知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只惡鬼竟然也會生病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是無奇不有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待他康復之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再將他送至亞德羅福斯將軍麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈來愈不安定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因為何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運改變實驗仍有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點得對弗肯保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪、達雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會有危險別扔下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓他睡個覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回國之後再對他進行再一次的命運改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加爾德島
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…正朝幻之谷去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯之民 龍神人的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他們給發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與艾薩克終於抵達一片滿是濃霧的原野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信幻之谷一定就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾幾何時艾薩克消失了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在這片濃霧中跟我走失了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我只要一心想著要抵達幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解開亞特蘭提斯之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必定能夠再次見到那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到她之後,我將…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃走是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂的天空騎士竟然會因為\N這點小事就產生動搖,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真不討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想過要你來喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你那麼說太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被可愛的女孩給討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小瞳嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看笑話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是無法原諒那傢伙…無法原諒家父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒拋家棄子的他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你不是還保韶著\N你父親的日誌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以丟掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻沒有那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在心裏某處\N你一定很希望能多瞭解他一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒辦法極度憎惡某個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你真的帶有那樣的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定也就不會那麼愛戴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你一定很想原諒你的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我只是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許只是不願意去承認自己是被父親給拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意原諒我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能通過這裏,馬上就會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,你就待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連浮游石都飛了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利甸,好好看著前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被撞上就沒戲唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你們在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到掌舵室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面出現浮游石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺了一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈的浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現阿斯多利亞高速艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅,耶莉雅,你們聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,我們隨時可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會將您弟弟帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙,上方被壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我們逼到地面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派魯,謝拉撒特好了沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,還不能出動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念一定能夠實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要無時無刻都強烈地希望著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,這個你拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆,請讓我能見到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家都能見到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都來到這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都要看到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后,您究竟期望我怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能在這裏被擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與父親您做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你究竟要到幻之谷去看什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯之門竟然開敔了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:57.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:06.04,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
